org.timepedia.chronoscope.client.render
Class CompositeAxisPanel

java.lang.Object
  org.timepedia.chronoscope.client.render.CompositeAxisPanel
All Implemented Interfaces:
GssElement, Panel
public final class CompositeAxisPanel
extends java.lang.Object
implements Panel, GssElement

A container that manages 0 or more AxisPanel objects. A CompositeAxisPanel can be assigned a CompositeAxisPanel.Position relative to its container. This panel is responsible for partitioning space for itself and allocating that space to each contained axis, as well as using its GSS axesProperties to fill the background of the panel when cleared.
